Class NullTraceEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.att.research.xacml.std.trace.NullTraceEngine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TraceEngine

    public class NullTraceEngine
extends java.lang.Object
implements TraceEngine
    Implements the TraceEngine interface to just ignore TraceEvents. This is the default implementation, returned by the default TraceEngineFactory.
